<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 09:16:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普威胁征收新关税，中国着眼于谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-eyes-negotiations-trump-threatens-new-tariffs-2024-12-13/</link><description>分析人士称，随着唐纳德·特朗普加大对中国的关税威胁，北京正采取行动，用自己的限制措施来击败下一任美国总统，并在全面贸易战之前让华盛顿坐到谈判桌前。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 08:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-eyes-negotiations-trump-threatens-new-tariffs-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国宁德时代为供应商提供资金支持以推动电池创新</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-catl-offers-suppliers-financial-support-drive-battery-innovation-2024-12-13/</link><description>中国宁德时代已告知供应商，愿意为他们提供资金支持，以加快电池材料和设备的技术创新，这是在残酷的电动汽车价格战中缓解其供应链压力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 08:01:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-catl-offers-suppliers-financial-support-drive-battery-innovation-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉在中国推出“真智能召唤”功能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-launches-actually-smart-summon-feature-china-2024-12-13/</link><description>美国汽车制造商特斯拉周五在中国推出了“其实智能召唤”功能。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 08:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-launches-actually-smart-summon-feature-china-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国针对台湾的新策略：演习“不敢说出自己的名字”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-new-tactic-against-taiwan-drills-that-dare-not-speak-their-name-2024-12-13/</link><description>官员和专家表示，北京在台湾这个它声称拥有主权的民主岛屿上公布了一项新策略：不张扬地进行大规模演习，以实现强化军事存在正常化，并让美国知道中国可以随时采取行动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:16:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-new-tactic-against-taiwan-drills-that-dare-not-speak-their-name-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>由于特朗普政策担忧和美元上涨，11 月份外资流出冲击亚洲债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-outflows-hit-asian-bonds-nov-trump-policy-concerns-dollars-rise-2024-12-13/</link><description>由于对即将上任的特朗普政府领导下的美国贸易政策发生变化的预期以及美元走强抑制了投资者的兴趣，11 月份亚洲债务市场七个月来首次出现外资流出。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 06:59:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-outflows-hit-asian-bonds-nov-trump-policy-concerns-dollars-rise-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国债券市场未来将面临更多经济阵痛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-bond-market-sees-more-economic-pain-ahead-2024-12-13/</link><description>中国债券投资者押注 2025 年经济不会出现奇迹般的复苏，这让他们与押注消费复苏的股市产生了分歧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 06:30:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-bond-market-sees-more-economic-pain-ahead-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国和埃及一致认为有必要促进中东和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-egypt-agree-need-promote-peace-middle-east-2024-12-13/</link><description>据媒体报道，中国外交部长王毅表示，北京同意埃及的观点，即两国应促进和平与谈判，以实现中东稳定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 06:19:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-egypt-agree-need-promote-peace-middle-east-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：全球降息让美元占据主导地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-13/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 05:41:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>安全担忧促使新西兰监管谁可以监控卫星</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/security-concerns-spur-new-zealand-regulate-who-can-monitor-satellites-2024-12-13/</link><description>新西兰政府周五表示，明年将通过立法，防止“不认同该国价值观”的实体将其用作监控卫星的基地。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 05:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/security-concerns-spur-new-zealand-regulate-who-can-monitor-satellites-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>前冠军瓦林卡接受澳网外卡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/former-champion-wawrinka-accepts-wildcard-australian-open-2024-12-13/</link><description>赛事组织者周五宣布，三届大满贯冠军斯坦·瓦林卡是九名持有外卡参加下个月澳大利亚网球公开赛的选手之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 05:07:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/former-champion-wawrinka-accepts-wildcard-australian-open-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，新加坡和越南公司正在就新海底电缆进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/singapore-vietnam-firms-talks-new-undersea-cables-sources-say-2024-12-13/</link><description>据知情人士透露，新加坡资产管理公司吉宝和越南企业集团 Sovico Group 正在讨论新的海底光缆计划，该计划将推动该地区的数据中心行业发展。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 04:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/singapore-vietnam-firms-talks-new-undersea-cables-sources-say-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>黄金将每周上涨，关注美联储政策决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-set-weekly-gain-with-focus-feds-policy-decision-2024-12-13/</link><description>周五金价小幅走高，预计周度上涨，原因是最近有报道称最大消费国中国恢复购买黄金，并提高了对美联储在 12 月 17 日至 18 日会议上降息的预期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 03:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-set-weekly-gain-with-focus-feds-policy-decision-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市走弱，美元因美国国债抛售而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-13/</link><description>由于缺乏中国刺激计划的细节令投资者感到失望，亚洲股市周五下跌，而由于美国对 2025 年降息的预期减弱，长期国债收益率出现一年来最大单周涨幅，美元受到提振。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 02:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥参议院批准应用程序驱动程序的工作福利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexican-senate-approves-work-benefits-app-drivers-2024-12-13/</link><description>墨西哥参议院周四批准了一项改革，以改善滴滴、Rappi 和 Uber 等网约车和送货服务司机的工作条件，确保他们获得社会保障和圣诞奖金等福利。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 02:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexican-senate-approves-work-benefits-app-drivers-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国考虑人民币贬值，特朗普贸易顾问警告不要操纵汇率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/trump-trade-adviser-warns-against-currency-manipulation-china-mulls-weaker-yuan-2024-12-12/</link><description>特朗普政府于2019年将中国列为汇率操纵国，这是美国政府自1994年以来首次做出这一决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:22:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/trump-trade-adviser-warns-against-currency-manipulation-china-mulls-weaker-yuan-2024-12-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>